---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="Privacy policy for smsaad.online"
  noIndex={false}
>
  <div class="pt-32 section bg-white dark:bg-surface-dark">
    <div class="container-custom max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="font-display font-black text-4xl text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-10">Last updated: December 2024</p>

      <div class="prose dark:prose-dark max-w-none space-y-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
        <p>This website, smsaad.online, is operated by SM SAAD. This page informs you of the policies regarding collection, use, and disclosure of information when you use this website.</p>

        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8">Information Collection</h2>
        <p>We collect information you provide directly when contacting us through our contact form. This includes your name, email address, and message content. This information is used solely to respond to your inquiry.</p>

        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8">Analytics</h2>
        <p>We use Cloudflare Web Analytics to understand how visitors use this site. This is privacy-preserving analytics that does not track individual users or use cookies.</p>

        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8">Cookies</h2>
        <p>This site uses localStorage (not cookies) for theme preferences, blog post likes, and bookmarks. This data stays on your device and is never transmitted to our servers.</p>

        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-2xl text-gray-900 dark:text-white mt-8">Contact</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about this policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@smsaad.online" class="text-brand-600 dark:text-brand-400">hello@smsaad.online</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
